Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为这样就能得意忘形了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋豆芽男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:27.94,Logo,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\shad0\c&H5F6371&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz18\pos(582,180)\b1}也算稍微有点优点
